unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-1", "frontend-2", "frontend-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "productcatalogservice-2"], "service_name": ["frontend", "productcatalogservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-06", "aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-01"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-21T04:10:13Z to 2025-06-21T04:33:13Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-21 04:10:13+00:00 to 2025-06-21 04:33:13+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的调用链数据，我已经完成了初始扫描分析。以下是关键发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\", \n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService的GetProduct操作延迟异常激增，从正常约10秒增加到3900万秒（约450天），延迟倍数超过3900倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\", \n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"出现大量'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'数据库错误，表明TiDB数据库Region不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务因ProductCatalogService不可用而返回HTTP 500错误，是错误传播的受害者\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"结账服务在调用ProductCatalogService获取商品信息时失败，导致订单处理失败\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**根因识别**: ProductCatalogService是系统故障的根源，具体表现为：\n- 极端延迟：GetProduct操作延迟从10秒激增至3900万秒\n- 数据库错误：TiDB数据库出现\"Region is unavailable\"错误\n\n**影响范围**: 故障通过依赖链传播：\n- ProductCatalogService → Frontend (用户界面)\n- ProductCatalogService → CheckoutService (结账流程)  \n- ProductCatalogService → RecommendationService (推荐服务)\n\n**关键指标**:\n- 延迟倍数：3900倍（显著异常）\n- 错误类型：数据库Region不可用错误\n- 影响服务：所有依赖ProductCatalogService的服务\n\n建议下一步深入分析TiDB数据库的Region可用性问题。", "log_analysis_findings": "基于对日志数据的全面扫描分析，我发现了明显的异常模式。以下是详细的发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000)\", \"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"code = Unknown\", \"failed to query product by id\", \"failed to get product recommendations\", \"could not retrieve product\", \"failed to complete the order\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库Region不可用导致产品查询失败 - 检测到 Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice日志显示：'failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'，出现频次高达495次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"依赖productcatalogservice失败导致的RPC调用错误 - 检测到 rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend服务日志显示多个错误：'failed to get product recommendations'、'could not retrieve product'，都指向productcatalogservice的数据库Region不可用问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice或相关订单服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"订单处理失败，无法获取产品信息 - 检测到 failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend日志显示：'failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to get product'，表明订单处理流程中断\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结**：\n1. **主要问题**：productcatalogservice的数据库Region不可用（Error 9005），这是根因\n2. **影响范围**：所有frontend实例都受到影响，无法获取产品信息和推荐\n3. **故障链**：productcatalogservice数据库问题 → frontend服务调用失败 → 用户购物车和订单功能异常\n4. **时间特征**：错误在04:10:54开始出现，持续到分析时间窗口结束", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取的指标数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。从数据中识别到多个显著的异常指标和故障模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"duration_99th\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"store_unhealth_count\", \"rrt\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypothese